# The runtime image needs exactly one file: the server fat jar. Exclude every target/ tree to keep
# the build context tiny, then re-include just strata-server's jar (ignore-dir-keep-one-file form).
**/target
!strata-server/target
strata-server/target/*
!strata-server/target/strata-server.jar
.git
.github
*.jfr
docs
tla
scripts
**/*.md
